column5: Anybody who's fished this lake recently I would love to here about it. Any comments or suggestions would be appreciated 1st time to the lake staying at pine portage lodge?

I would appreciate a report when you return, Im going up in Sept.We fished the lake a couple of years ago and loved it, caught most walleye on a jig head with minnows. Seems like yellow is always a good color on that lake from talking with regulars
